ast_modified": 1732002052, "replies": 56, "id": 1090853}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_large.png?m=1630643913", "name": "apple", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_normal.png?m=1630643913", "title": "Apple", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/apple", "topics": 27456, "footer": "", "header": "设计了 <a href=\"/go/watch\">Apple Watch</a>，<a href=\"/go/ipad\">iPad</a>，<a href=\"/go/iphone\">iPhone</a>，<a href=\"/go/imac\">iMac</a> 及 <a href=\"/go/mbp\">MacBook Pro</a> 等电子产品的美国公司。", "title_alternative": "Apple", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_mini.png?m=1630643913", "stars": 3071, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 184, "parent_node_name": "hardware"}, "member": {"id": 647743, "username": "GeekGuru", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/GeekGuru", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/32ad/39d1/647743_mini.png?m=1719759557", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/32ad/39d1/647743_normal.png?m=1719759557", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/32ad/39d1/647743_large.png?m=1719759557", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/32ad/39d1/647743_xlarge.png?m=1719759557", "created": 1694241478, "last_modified": 1719759557}, "last_reply_by": "superrichman", "last_touched": 1732068741, "title": "M4 Mac mini 这么火，但是可能存在重大 BUG", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1090929", "created": 1732010452, "deleted": 0, "content": "目前观察到的问题：\r\n\r\n1. 风扇转速非常保守，本次电源集成在主板上层，顶盖比较热的时候，转速依然只有 1000 转。\r\n\r\n2. CPU 和 GPU 的功率分配不合理，这个可能是软件问题，举例 Adobe 倒入大量图片时，GPU 几乎不出力，但 CPU 可以跑到 108 度以上的高温。\r\n\r\n3. 黑猫群看到的：M4 PRO/MAX 芯片 Kernel Panic 的问题。\r\n黑猫的情况描述：\r\n黑猫的两台 M4 PRO 芯片的 MBP 上运行无人深空或 Stray 或其他游戏时有较大概率会遇到死机并重启（ Kernel Panic 提示 cpu x caller ）。区区一个游戏导致了整只电脑的崩溃很罕见也很严重，不免联想到可能是硬件缺陷，但也可能是单纯 OS 的问题。", "content_rendered": "<p>目前观察到的问题：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>风扇转速非常保守，本次电源集成在主板上层，顶盖比较热的时候，转速依然只有 1000 转。</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>CPU 和 GPU 的功率分配不合理，这个可能是软件问题，举例 Adobe 倒入大量图片时，GPU 几乎不出力，但 CPU 可以跑到 108 度以上的高温。</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>黑猫群看到的：M4 PRO/MAX 芯片 Kernel Panic 的问题。\n黑猫的情况描述：\n黑猫的两台 M4 PRO 芯片的 MBP 上运行无人深空或 Stray 或其他游戏时有较大概率会遇到死机并重启（ Kernel Panic 提示 cpu x caller ）。区区一个游戏导致了整只电脑的崩溃很罕见也很严重，不免联想到可能是硬件缺陷，但也可能是单纯 OS 的问题。</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n", "last_modified": 1732010452, "replies": 52, "id": 1090929}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/b6d7/67d2/22_large.png?m=1649080598", "name": "macos", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/b6d7/67d2/22_normal.png?m=1649080598", "title": "macOS", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/macos", "topics": 22416, "footer": "<a href=\"/mbp\">MacBook Pro</a> 及 <a href=\"/go/imac\">iMac</a> 等 <a href=\"/go/apple\">Apple</a> 公司设计的计算机所运行的操作系统。<a href=\"/go/idev\">iOS</a> 的基础。", "header": "The world’s most advanced desktop operating system.", "title_alternative": "macOS", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/b6d7/67d2/22_mini.png?m=1649080598", "stars": 5286, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 22, "parent_node_name": "os"}, "member": {"id": 286232, "username": "Cheesen", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/Cheesen", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a254/9302/286232_mini.png?m=1730283590", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a254/9302/286232_normal.png?m=1730283590", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a254/9302/286232_large.png?m=1730283590", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a254/9302/286232_xlarge.png?m=1730283590", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a254/9302/286232_xlarge.png?m=1730283590", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a254/9302/286232_xlarge.png?m=1730283590", "created": 1516787663, "last_modified": 1730283590}, "last_reply_by": "ldlywt", "last_touched": 1732038834, "title": "Mac App Store 里面有没有良心的，无广告的，无内购的优质 APP", 